    <title type="html"><![CDATA[View Mt Blanc while climbing on Salève]]></title>
    <link href="http://playdegex.github.io/2011/04/view-mt-blanc-while-climbing-on-saleve/"/>
    <updated>2011-04-03T20:00:55+02:00</updated>
    <id>http://playdegex.github.io/2011/04/view-mt-blanc-while-climbing-on-saleve</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vMhpXrffCBo/TZiuzgubxLI/AAAAAAAAzkI/WXsEF_474po/s1600/DSCN3196.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vMhpXrffCBo/TZiuzgubxLI/AAAAAAAAzkI/WXsEF_474po/s320/DSCN3196.JPG" width="320" /></a></div>


<p>The <span class="pp-place-title"><span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sal%C3%A8ve">Salève</a> is the 1400m mountain right next to Geneva. It&rsquo;s easy to reach with public transport and then can be scaled with the <a href="http://www.telepheriquedusaleve.com/">cable car</a> or alternatively you can just drive up. Apart from the obvious <a href="http://www.destination-montagne.ch/En/Articles/Paths_of_Saleve.html">walking</a> and view-taking to do there is a small see-saw at the kiosk at the top of the cable car. The <a href="http://www.lamuraz.com/387_en.html">Auberge des Montagnards</a> in Croisette has a terrace and small climbing frame (which is reassuringly close to the restaurant&rsquo;s tables) looking out to Mt Blanc, they also have chickens and rabbit as a useful diversion.</span></span><a href=""><strong></strong></a><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AK4UWsYerFs/TZivDesYRAI/AAAAAAAAzkM/G7X0EV4GFSc/s1600/DSCN3198.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AK4UWsYerFs/TZivDesYRAI/AAAAAAAAzkM/G7X0EV4GFSc/s320/DSCN3198.JPG" width="320" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aM3bNU-3q04/TZivVqLMRWI/AAAAAAAAzkU/-_zF6LRcWV0/s1600/DSCN3181.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aM3bNU-3q04/TZivVqLMRWI/AAAAAAAAzkU/-_zF6LRcWV0/s320/DSCN3181.JPG" width="320" /></a></div></p>
